Create a secret : 
  Imperative way : kubectl create secret genereic secret-name --from-literal
                                                                --from-literal
    kubectl create secret generic --from-file=<path to-file> 
  Declarative way: kubectl create -f  
  
 To encode  echo -n "" | base64
 To decode echo -n ""  | base64 --decode 
 kubectl get secrets
 kubectl describe secrets
 kubectl get secrets ap-secret -o yaml
 
